              />
            </svg>
            2. Create your webhook URL
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base/7 text-gray-600">
            <p class="flex-auto">
              Gitspatch generates a secret URL which will trigger workflows when
              called. Of course, the payload is forwarded to the CI.
            </p>
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <dt
            class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900"
          >
            <svg
              class="size-5 flex-none text-indigo-600"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              data-slot="icon"
            >
              <path
