          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base/7 text-gray-600">
            <p class="flex-auto">
              Leverage GitHub Actions' full power: run scripts, use containers,
              automate anything. Zero infrastructure, instant monitoring.
            </p>
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto mt-32 max-w-7xl sm:mt-56 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div
      class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-gray-900 px-6 py-24 text-center shadow-2xl sm:rounded-3xl sm:px-16"
